high_descs: Turn right and head across the passage to reach the room on the left and face the cabinet.
Pick up the cloth from the cabinet.
Turn around and head right to walk down the passage and turn right to reach the shelf under the TV,
Put the cloth in the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put the cloth in the shelf.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the cabinet to your left.
Pick up cloth from the cabinet.
Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Moving cloth from one location to another.

high_descs: Turn right and head straight, make left and then again hang left towards the cabinet
Pick up cloth from the cabinet
Turn around and going straight, proceed to turn to the left towards the shelf
anns.task_desc: Shifting cloth from one place to another
